{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"This machine, which we all have residing in our skulls,"},{"time":3000,"text":"reminds me of an aphorism, of a"},{"time":6000,"text":"comment of Woody Allen"},{"time":8000,"text":"to ask about what is the very best thing to have within your skull."},{"time":10000,"text":"And it's this machine."},{"time":12000,"text":"And it's constructed for change. It's all about change."},{"time":15000,"text":"It confers on us the ability to do things tomorrow that we can't do today,"},{"time":18000,"text":"things today that we couldn't do yesterday."},{"time":20000,"text":"And of course it's born stupid."}]},{"cues":[{"time":22000,"text":"The last time you were in the presence of a baby --"},{"time":24000,"text":"this happens to be my granddaughter, Mitra."},{"time":27000,"text":"Isn't she fabulous?"},{"time":29000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":30000,"text":"But nonetheless when she popped out"},{"time":32000,"text":"despite the fact that her brain had actually been progressing"},{"time":34000,"text":"in its development for several months before"},{"time":36000,"text":"on the basis of her experiences in the womb --"},{"time":38000,"text":"nonetheless she had very limited abilities,"},{"time":40000,"text":"as does every infant"},{"time":42000,"text":"at the time of normal, natural full-term birth."},{"time":45000,"text":"If we were to assay her perceptual abilities, they would be crude."},{"time":49000,"text":"There is no real indication that there is any real thinking going on."},{"time":52000,"text":"In fact there is little evidence that there is any"},{"time":55000,"text":"cognitive ability in a very young infant."},{"time":58000,"text":"Infants don't respond to much."},{"time":60000,"text":"There is not really much of an indication in fact that there is a person on board."},{"time":63000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":66000,"text":"And they can only in a very primitive way, and in a very limited way"},{"time":69000,"text":"control their movements."}]},{"cues":[{"time":70000,"text":"It would be several months before this infant"},{"time":72000,"text":"could do something as simple as reach out and grasp"},{"time":74000,"text":"under voluntary control an object and retrieve it,"},{"time":76000,"text":"usually to the mouth."},{"time":78000,"text":"And it will be some months beforeward,"},{"time":80000,"text":"and we see a long steady progression"},{"time":83000,"text":"of the evolution from the first wiggles,"},{"time":85000,"text":"to rolling over, and sitting up, and crawling,"},{"time":87000,"text":"standing, walking,"},{"time":89000,"text":"before we get to that magical point"},{"time":91000,"text":"in which we can motate in the world."},{"time":93000,"text":"And yet, when we look forward in the brain"},{"time":95000,"text":"we see really remarkable advance."},{"time":98000,"text":"By this age the brain can actually store."},{"time":100000,"text":"It has stored, recorded,"},{"time":102000,"text":"can fastly retrieve"},{"time":104000,"text":"the meanings of thousands,"},{"time":106000,"text":"tens of thousands of objects,"},{"time":108000,"text":"actions, and their relationships in the world."},{"time":110000,"text":"And those relationships can in fact be constructed in hundreds of thousands,"},{"time":113000,"text":"potentially millions of ways."},{"time":115000,"text":"By this age the brain controls very refined perceptual abilities."},{"time":120000,"text":"And it actually has a growing repertoire of cognitive skills."},{"time":123000,"text":"This brain is very much a thinking machine."},{"time":126000,"text":"And by this age there is absolutely no question"},{"time":129000,"text":"that this brain, it has a person on board."},{"time":133000,"text":"And in fact at this age it is substantially controlling its own self-development."},{"time":137000,"text":"And by this age we see a remarkable evolution"},{"time":139000,"text":"in its capacity to control movement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":142000,"text":"Now movement has advanced to the point"},{"time":144000,"text":"where it can actually control movement simultaneously,"},{"time":147000,"text":"in a complex sequence, in complex ways"},{"time":149000,"text":"as would be required for example"},{"time":151000,"text":"for playing a complicated game,"},{"time":153000,"text":"like soccer."},{"time":155000,"text":"Now this boy can bounce a soccer ball on his head."},{"time":158000,"text":"And where this boy comes from, Sao Paulo, Brazil,"},{"time":160000,"text":"about 40 percent of boys of his age have this ability."},{"time":164000,"text":"You could go out into the community in Monterey,"},{"time":168000,"text":"and you'd have difficulty finding a boy that has this ability."},{"time":171000,"text":"And if you did he'd probably be from Sao Paulo."},{"time":174000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":175000,"text":"That's all another way of saying"},{"time":177000,"text":"that our individual skills and abilities"},{"time":179000,"text":"are very much shaped by our environments."},{"time":181000,"text":"That environment extends into our contemporary culture,"},{"time":184000,"text":"the thing our brain is challenged with."},{"time":186000,"text":"Because what we've done in our personal evolutions"},{"time":188000,"text":"is build up a large repertoire of specific skills and abilities"},{"time":192000,"text":"that are specific to our own individual histories."},{"time":194000,"text":"And in fact they result in a wonderful"},{"time":196000,"text":"differentiation in humankind,"},{"time":199000,"text":"in the way that, in fact, no two of us"},{"time":201000,"text":"are quite alike."},{"time":203000,"text":"Every one of us has a different set of acquired skills and abilities"},{"time":206000,"text":"that all derive out of the plasticity,"},{"time":208000,"text":"the adaptability of this really remarkable adaptive machine."},{"time":213000,"text":"In an adult brain of course we've built up"},{"time":216000,"text":"a large repertoire of mastered skills and abilities"},{"time":218000,"text":"that we can perform more or less automatically from memory,"},{"time":221000,"text":"and that define us as acting, moving, thinking creatures."}]},{"cues":[{"time":226000,"text":"Now we study this,"},{"time":228000,"text":"as the nerdy, laboratory, university-based scientists that we are,"},{"time":231000,"text":"by engaging the brains"},{"time":233000,"text":"of animals like rats, or monkeys,"},{"time":236000,"text":"or of this particularly curious creature --"},{"time":239000,"text":"one of the more bizarre forms of life on earth --"},{"time":242000,"text":"to engage them in learning new skills and abilities."},{"time":245000,"text":"And we try to track the changes that occur"},{"time":247000,"text":"as the new skill or ability is acquired."},{"time":249000,"text":"In fact we do this in individuals"},{"time":252000,"text":"of any age, in these different species --"},{"time":254000,"text":"that is to say from infancies,"},{"time":256000,"text":"infancy up to adulthood and old age."},{"time":260000,"text":"So we might engage a rat, for example,"},{"time":262000,"text":"to acquire a new skill or ability"},{"time":264000,"text":"that might involve the rat using its paw"},{"time":267000,"text":"to master particular manual grasp behaviors"},{"time":269000,"text":"just like we might examine a child"},{"time":272000,"text":"and their ability to acquire the sub-skills,"},{"time":274000,"text":"or the general overall skill of accomplishing something"},{"time":276000,"text":"like mastering the ability to read."},{"time":279000,"text":"Or you might look in an older individual"},{"time":281000,"text":"who has mastered a complex set of abilities"},{"time":283000,"text":"that might relate to reading musical notation"},{"time":285000,"text":"or performing the mechanical acts of performance"},{"time":288000,"text":"that apply to musical performance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":291000,"text":"From these studies we defined two great epochs"},{"time":294000,"text":"of the plastic history of the brain."},{"time":297000,"text":"The first great epoch is commonly called the \"Critical Period.\""},{"time":300000,"text":"And that is the period in which the brain is setting up"},{"time":302000,"text":"in its initial form its basic processing machinery."},{"time":305000,"text":"This is actually a period of dramatic change"},{"time":308000,"text":"in which it doesn't take learning, per se, to drive"},{"time":311000,"text":"the initial differentiation of the machinery of the brain."},{"time":314000,"text":"All it takes for example in the sound domain,"},{"time":317000,"text":"is exposure to sound."},{"time":319000,"text":"And the brain actually is at the mercy"},{"time":321000,"text":"of the sound environment in which it is reared."},{"time":325000,"text":"So for example I can rear an animal"},{"time":327000,"text":"in an environment in which there is meaningless dumb sound,"},{"time":331000,"text":"a repertoire of sound that I make up,"},{"time":334000,"text":"that I make, just by exposure, artificially important"},{"time":336000,"text":"to the animal and its young brain."},{"time":339000,"text":"And what I see is that the animal's brain sets up"},{"time":341000,"text":"its initial processing of that sound"},{"time":343000,"text":"in a form that's idealized, within the limits of its processing achievements"},{"time":347000,"text":"to represent it in an organized and orderly way."},{"time":351000,"text":"The sound doesn't have to be valuable to the animal:"},{"time":354000,"text":"I could raise the animal in something that could be hypothetically valuable,"},{"time":357000,"text":"like the sounds that simulate"},{"time":359000,"text":"the sounds of a native language of a child."},{"time":362000,"text":"And I see the brain actually develop a processor that is specialized --"},{"time":365000,"text":"specialized for that complex array, a repertoire of sounds."},{"time":368000,"text":"It actually exaggerates their separateness of representation,"},{"time":371000,"text":"in multi-dimensional neuronal representational terms."}]},{"cues":[{"time":375000,"text":"Or I can expose the animal to a completely meaningless and destructive sound."},{"time":380000,"text":"I can raise an animal under conditions"},{"time":382000,"text":"that would be equivalent to raising a baby"},{"time":384000,"text":"under a moderately loud ceiling fan,"},{"time":386000,"text":"in the presence of continuous noise."},{"time":388000,"text":"And when I do that I actually specialize the brain"},{"time":391000,"text":"to be a master processor for that meaningless sound."},{"time":395000,"text":"And I frustrate its ability"},{"time":397000,"text":"to represent any meaningful sound as a consequence."},{"time":400000,"text":"Such things in the early history of babies"},{"time":402000,"text":"occur in real babies."},{"time":404000,"text":"And they account for, for example"},{"time":407000,"text":"the beautiful evolution of a language-specific processor"},{"time":410000,"text":"in every normally developing baby."},{"time":413000,"text":"And so they also account for"},{"time":415000,"text":"development of defective processing"},{"time":417000,"text":"in a substantial population of children"},{"time":420000,"text":"who are more limited, as a consequence,"},{"time":422000,"text":"in their language abilities at an older age."}]},{"cues":[{"time":426000,"text":"Now in this early period of plasticity"},{"time":429000,"text":"the brain actually changes outside of a learning context."},{"time":432000,"text":"I don't have to be paying attention to what I hear."},{"time":435000,"text":"The input doesn't really have to be meaningful."},{"time":438000,"text":"I don't have to be in a behavioral context."},{"time":441000,"text":"This is required so the brain sets up it's processing"},{"time":444000,"text":"so that it can act differentially,"},{"time":446000,"text":"so that it can act selectively,"},{"time":448000,"text":"so that the creature that wears it, that carries it,"},{"time":452000,"text":"can begin to operate on it in a selective way."},{"time":455000,"text":"In the next great epoch of life, which applies for most of life,"},{"time":459000,"text":"the brain is actually refining its machinery"},{"time":462000,"text":"as it masters a wide repertoire of skills and abilities."},{"time":464000,"text":"And in this epoch,"},{"time":466000,"text":"which extends from late in the first year of life to death;"},{"time":470000,"text":"it's actually doing this under behavioral control."},{"time":472000,"text":"And that's another way of saying"},{"time":474000,"text":"the brain has strategies that define"},{"time":477000,"text":"the significance of the input to the brain."},{"time":479000,"text":"And it's focusing on skill after skill,"},{"time":481000,"text":"or ability after ability,"},{"time":485000,"text":"under specific attentional control."},{"time":487000,"text":"It's a function of whether a goal in a behavior is achieved"},{"time":490000,"text":"or whether the individual is rewarded in the behavior."},{"time":495000,"text":"This is actually very powerful."},{"time":498000,"text":"This lifelong capacity for plasticity, for brain change,"},{"time":500000,"text":"is powerfully expressed."},{"time":502000,"text":"It is the basis of our real differentiation,"},{"time":504000,"text":"one individual from another."},{"time":506000,"text":"You can look down in the brain of an animal"},{"time":508000,"text":"that's engaged in a specific skill,"},{"time":510000,"text":"and you can witness or document this change on a variety of levels."}]},{"cues":[{"time":513000,"text":"So here is a very simple experiment."},{"time":515000,"text":"It was actually conducted about five years ago"},{"time":517000,"text":"in collaboration with scientists from the University of Provence"},{"time":520000,"text":"in Marseilles."},{"time":522000,"text":"It's a very simple experiment where a monkey has been trained"},{"time":524000,"text":"in a task that involves it manipulating a tool"},{"time":528000,"text":"that's equivalent in its difficulty"},{"time":530000,"text":"to a child learning to manipulate or handle a spoon."},{"time":532000,"text":"The monkey actually mastered the task"},{"time":534000,"text":"in about 700 practice tries."},{"time":537000,"text":"So in the beginning the monkey could not perform this task at all."},{"time":540000,"text":"It had a success rate of about one in eight tries."},{"time":543000,"text":"Those tries were elaborate."},{"time":545000,"text":"Each attempt was substantially different from the other."},{"time":548000,"text":"But the monkey gradually developed a strategy."},{"time":551000,"text":"And 700 or so tries later"},{"time":553000,"text":"the monkey is performing it flawlessly -- never fails."},{"time":556000,"text":"He's successful in his retrieval of food with this tool every time."},{"time":559000,"text":"At this point the task is being performed"},{"time":561000,"text":"in a beautifully stereotyped way:"},{"time":564000,"text":"very beautifully regulated and highly repeated, trial to trial."}]},{"cues":[{"time":567000,"text":"We can look down in the brain of the monkey."},{"time":569000,"text":"And we see that it's distorted."},{"time":571000,"text":"We can track these changes, and have tracked these changes"},{"time":573000,"text":"in many such behaviors across time."},{"time":575000,"text":"And here we see the distortion"},{"time":578000,"text":"reflected in the map of the skin surfaces of the hand of the monkey."},{"time":581000,"text":"Now this is a map, down in the surface of the brain,"},{"time":584000,"text":"in which, in a very elaborate experiment we've reconstructed the responses,"},{"time":587000,"text":"location by location,"},{"time":589000,"text":"in a highly detailed response mapping of the responses of its neurons."},{"time":593000,"text":"We see here a reconstruction of how"},{"time":595000,"text":"the hand is represented in the brain."},{"time":597000,"text":"We've actually distorted the map by the exercise."},{"time":600000,"text":"And that is indicated in the pink. We have a couple fingertip surfaces that are larger."},{"time":604000,"text":"These are the surfaces the monkey is using to manipulate the tool."},{"time":608000,"text":"If we look at the selectivity of responses"},{"time":610000,"text":"in the cortex of the monkey,"},{"time":612000,"text":"we see that the monkey has actually changed the filter characteristics"},{"time":615000,"text":"which represents input from the skin"},{"time":617000,"text":"of the fingertips that are engaged."},{"time":619000,"text":"In other words there is still a single, simple representation of the fingertips"},{"time":622000,"text":"in this most organized of cortical areas"},{"time":624000,"text":"of the surface of the skin of the body."},{"time":626000,"text":"Monkey has like you have."},{"time":629000,"text":"And yet now it's represented in substantially finer grain."},{"time":632000,"text":"The monkey is getting more detailed information from these surfaces."},{"time":635000,"text":"And that is an unknown -- unsuspected, maybe, by you --"},{"time":638000,"text":"part of acquiring the skill or ability."}]},{"cues":[{"time":641000,"text":"Now actually we've looked in several different cortical areas"},{"time":644000,"text":"in the monkey learning this task."},{"time":646000,"text":"And each one of them changes in ways that are specific"},{"time":648000,"text":"to the skill or ability."},{"time":650000,"text":"So for example we can look to the cortical area"},{"time":653000,"text":"that represents input that's controlling the posture of the monkey."},{"time":656000,"text":"We look in cortical areas that control specific movements,"},{"time":658000,"text":"and the sequences of movements"},{"time":660000,"text":"that are required in the behavior, and so forth."},{"time":662000,"text":"They are all remodeled. They all become specialized for the task at hand."},{"time":666000,"text":"There are 15 or 20 cortical areas that are changed specifically"},{"time":669000,"text":"when you learn a simple skill like this."},{"time":672000,"text":"And that represents in your brain, really massive change."},{"time":676000,"text":"It represents the change in a reliable way"},{"time":679000,"text":"of the responses of tens of millions,"},{"time":681000,"text":"possibly hundreds of millions of neurons in your brain."},{"time":684000,"text":"It represents changes"},{"time":686000,"text":"of hundreds of millions, possibly billions"},{"time":688000,"text":"of synaptic connections in your brain."},{"time":690000,"text":"This is constructed by physical change."},{"time":693000,"text":"And the level of construction that occurs is massive."},{"time":696000,"text":"Think about the changes that occur in the brain of a child"},{"time":699000,"text":"through the course of acquiring their movement behavior abilities in general."},{"time":703000,"text":"Or acquiring their native language abilities."},{"time":705000,"text":"The changes are massive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":709000,"text":"What it's all about is the selective representations"},{"time":711000,"text":"of things that are important to the brain."},{"time":713000,"text":"Because in most of the life of the brain"},{"time":716000,"text":"this is under control of behavioral context."},{"time":718000,"text":"It's what you pay attention to."},{"time":720000,"text":"It's what's rewarding to you."},{"time":722000,"text":"It's what the brain regards, itself,"},{"time":724000,"text":"as positive and important to you."},{"time":726000,"text":"It's all about cortical processing"},{"time":728000,"text":"and forebrain specialization."},{"time":730000,"text":"And that underlies your specialization."},{"time":732000,"text":"That is why you, in your many skills and abilities,"},{"time":734000,"text":"are a unique specialist:"},{"time":736000,"text":"a specialist that's vastly different"},{"time":738000,"text":"in your physical brain in detail"},{"time":740000,"text":"than the brain of an individual 100 years ago;"},{"time":743000,"text":"enormously different in the details"},{"time":746000,"text":"from the brain of the average individual 1,000 years ago."},{"time":750000,"text":"Now, one of the characteristics of this change process"},{"time":754000,"text":"is that information is always related"},{"time":757000,"text":"to other inputs or information that is occurring"},{"time":759000,"text":"in immediate time, in context."},{"time":762000,"text":"And that's because the brain is constructing representations of things"},{"time":765000,"text":"that are correlated in little moments of time"},{"time":768000,"text":"and that relate to one another in little moments of successive time."},{"time":771000,"text":"The brain is recording all information"},{"time":773000,"text":"and driving all change"},{"time":775000,"text":"in temporal context."},{"time":777000,"text":"Now overwhelmingly the most powerful context"},{"time":779000,"text":"that's occurred in your brain is you."},{"time":782000,"text":"Billions of events have occurred in your history"},{"time":786000,"text":"that are related in time to yourself"},{"time":788000,"text":"as the receiver,"},{"time":790000,"text":"or yourself as the actor, yourself as the thinker,"},{"time":792000,"text":"yourself as the mover."},{"time":795000,"text":"Billions of times little pieces of sensation have come in"},{"time":798000,"text":"from the surface of your body"},{"time":800000,"text":"that are always associated with you as the receiver,"},{"time":803000,"text":"and that result in"},{"time":805000,"text":"the embodiment of you."},{"time":808000,"text":"You are constructed, your self is constructed"},{"time":811000,"text":"from these billions of events."},{"time":813000,"text":"It's constructed. It's created in your brain."},{"time":816000,"text":"And it's created in the brain via physical change."},{"time":819000,"text":"This is a marvelously constructed thing"},{"time":822000,"text":"that results in individual form"},{"time":825000,"text":"because each one of us has vastly different histories,"},{"time":827000,"text":"and vastly different experiences,"},{"time":829000,"text":"that drive in to us this marvelous differentiation of self,"},{"time":833000,"text":"of personhood."}]},{"cues":[{"time":835000,"text":"Now we've used this research"},{"time":837000,"text":"to try to understand not just how a normal person develops,"},{"time":840000,"text":"and elaborates their skills and abilities,"},{"time":842000,"text":"but also try to understand"},{"time":844000,"text":"the origins of impairment,"},{"time":847000,"text":"and the origins of differences or variations"},{"time":850000,"text":"that might limit the capacities of a child, or an adult."},{"time":853000,"text":"I'm going to talk about using these strategies"},{"time":856000,"text":"to actually design brain plasticity-based"},{"time":858000,"text":"approach to drive corrections in the machinery of a child"},{"time":863000,"text":"that increases the competence of the child"},{"time":866000,"text":"as a language receiver and user"},{"time":868000,"text":"and, thereafter, as a reader."},{"time":870000,"text":"And I'm going to talk about experiments that involve"},{"time":872000,"text":"actually using this brain science,"},{"time":874000,"text":"first of all to understand how it contributes to the loss of function as we age."},{"time":877000,"text":"And then, by using it in a targeted approach"},{"time":882000,"text":"we're going to try to differentiate"},{"time":884000,"text":"the machinery to recover function in old age."}]},{"cues":[{"time":889000,"text":"So the first example I'm going to talk about"},{"time":891000,"text":"relates to children with learning impairments."},{"time":893000,"text":"We now have a large body of literature"},{"time":895000,"text":"that demonstrates that the fundamental"},{"time":897000,"text":"problem that occurs in the majority of children"},{"time":899000,"text":"that have early language impairments,"},{"time":901000,"text":"and that are going to struggle to learn to read,"},{"time":903000,"text":"is that their language processor"},{"time":905000,"text":"is created in a defective form."},{"time":907000,"text":"And the reason that it rises in a defective form"},{"time":910000,"text":"is because early in the baby's brain's life"},{"time":914000,"text":"the machine process is noisy."},{"time":916000,"text":"It's that simple."},{"time":918000,"text":"It's a signal-to-noise problem. Okay?"},{"time":920000,"text":"And there are a lot of things that contribute to that."},{"time":922000,"text":"There are numerous inherited faults"},{"time":924000,"text":"that could make the machine process noisier."},{"time":927000,"text":"Now I might say the noise problem could also occur"},{"time":930000,"text":"on the basis of information provided"},{"time":933000,"text":"in the world from the ears."}]},{"cues":[{"time":936000,"text":"If any -- those of you who are older in the audience know"},{"time":939000,"text":"that when I was a child we understood that a child born with a cleft palate"},{"time":943000,"text":"was born with what we called mental retardation."},{"time":946000,"text":"We knew that they were going to be slow cognitively;"},{"time":950000,"text":"we knew they were going to struggle to learn to develop normal language abilities;"},{"time":953000,"text":"and we knew that they were going to struggle to learn to read."},{"time":957000,"text":"Most of them would be intellectual and academic failures."},{"time":961000,"text":"That's disappeared. That no longer applies."},{"time":964000,"text":"That inherited weakness, that inherited condition"},{"time":966000,"text":"has evaporated."},{"time":968000,"text":"We don't hear about that anymore. Where did it go?"},{"time":971000,"text":"Well, it was understood by a Dutch surgeon,"},{"time":973000,"text":"about 35 years ago,"},{"time":975000,"text":"that if you simply fix the problem early enough,"},{"time":978000,"text":"when the brain is still in this initial plastic period"},{"time":980000,"text":"so it can set up this machinery adequately,"},{"time":983000,"text":"in this initial set up time in the critical period,"},{"time":985000,"text":"none of that happens."},{"time":987000,"text":"What are you doing by operating on the cleft palate to correct it?"},{"time":990000,"text":"You're basically opening up"},{"time":992000,"text":"the tubes that drain fluid from the middle ears,"},{"time":994000,"text":"which have had them reliably full."},{"time":997000,"text":"Every sound the child hears uncorrected is muffled."},{"time":999000,"text":"It's degraded."},{"time":1001000,"text":"The child's native language is such a case is not English."},{"time":1004000,"text":"It's not Japanese."},{"time":1006000,"text":"It's muffled English. It's degraded Japanese."},{"time":1009000,"text":"It's crap."},{"time":1011000,"text":"And the brain specializes for it."},{"time":1013000,"text":"It creates a representation of language crap."},{"time":1016000,"text":"And then the child is stuck with it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1018000,"text":"Now the crap doesn't just happen in the ear."},{"time":1021000,"text":"It can also happen in the brain."},{"time":1023000,"text":"The brain itself can be noisy. It's commonly noisy."},{"time":1027000,"text":"There are many inherited faults that can make it noisier."},{"time":1030000,"text":"And the native language for a child with such a brain"},{"time":1033000,"text":"is degraded."},{"time":1034000,"text":"It's not English. It's noisy English."},{"time":1038000,"text":"And that results in defective representations of sounds of words --"},{"time":1042000,"text":"not normal -- a different strategy,"},{"time":1045000,"text":"by a machine that has different time constants and different space constants."},{"time":1048000,"text":"And you can look in the brain of such a child and record those time constants."},{"time":1051000,"text":"They are about an order of magnitude longer,"},{"time":1054000,"text":"about 11 times longer in duration on average,"},{"time":1057000,"text":"than in a normal child."},{"time":1059000,"text":"Space constants are about three times greater."},{"time":1062000,"text":"Such a child will have memory and cognitive deficits"},{"time":1064000,"text":"in this domain."},{"time":1066000,"text":"Of course they will. Because as a receiver of language,"},{"time":1069000,"text":"they are receiving it and representing it,"},{"time":1071000,"text":"and in information it's representing crap."},{"time":1075000,"text":"And they are going to have poor reading skills."},{"time":1077000,"text":"Because reading is dependent upon the translation of word sounds"},{"time":1080000,"text":"into this orthographic or visual"},{"time":1083000,"text":"representational form."},{"time":1085000,"text":"If you don't have a brain representation of word sounds"},{"time":1087000,"text":"that translation makes no sense."},{"time":1090000,"text":"And you are going to have corresponding abnormal neurology."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1093000,"text":"Then these children increasingly"},{"time":1095000,"text":"in evaluation after evaluation,"},{"time":1097000,"text":"in their operations in language, and their operations in reading --"},{"time":1099000,"text":"we document that abnormal neurology."},{"time":1104000,"text":"The point is is that you can train the brain out of this."},{"time":1106000,"text":"A way to think about this is you can actually re-refine"},{"time":1108000,"text":"the processing capacity of the machinery"},{"time":1110000,"text":"by changing it."},{"time":1112000,"text":"Changing it in detail. It takes about 30 hours on the average."},{"time":1115000,"text":"And we've accomplished that in about 430,000 kids today."},{"time":1119000,"text":"Actually, probably about 15,000 children are being trained as we speak."},{"time":1124000,"text":"And actually when you look at the impacts, the impacts are substantial."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1127000,"text":"So here we're looking at the normal distribution."},{"time":1129000,"text":"What we're most interested in is these kids on the left side of the distribution."},{"time":1131000,"text":"This is from about 3,000 children."},{"time":1133000,"text":"You can see that most of the children on the left side of the distribution"},{"time":1136000,"text":"are moving into the middle or the right."},{"time":1138000,"text":"This is in a broad assessment of their language abilities."},{"time":1141000,"text":"This is like an IQ test for language."},{"time":1143000,"text":"The impact in the distribution, if you trained every child"},{"time":1146000,"text":"in the United States, would be to shift the whole distribution to the right"},{"time":1149000,"text":"and narrow the distribution."},{"time":1151000,"text":"This is a substantially large impact."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1153000,"text":"Think of a classroom of children in the language arts."},{"time":1156000,"text":"Think of the children on the slow side of the class."},{"time":1159000,"text":"We have the potential to move most of those children"},{"time":1161000,"text":"to the middle or to the right side."},{"time":1163000,"text":"In addition to accurate language training"},{"time":1165000,"text":"it also fixes memory and cognition"},{"time":1167000,"text":"speech fluency and speech production."},{"time":1170000,"text":"And an important language dependent skill is enabled by this training --"},{"time":1173000,"text":"that is to say reading."},{"time":1174000,"text":"And to a large extent it fixes the brain."},{"time":1176000,"text":"You can look down in the brain of a child"},{"time":1179000,"text":"in a variety of tasks that scientists have at Stanford,"},{"time":1182000,"text":"and MIT, and UCSF, and UCLA, and a number of other institutions."},{"time":1188000,"text":"And children operating in various language behaviors,"},{"time":1191000,"text":"or in various reading behaviors,"},{"time":1193000,"text":"you see for the most extent,"},{"time":1195000,"text":"for most children, their neuronal responses,"},{"time":1197000,"text":"complexly abnormal before you start,"},{"time":1199000,"text":"are normalized by the training."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1202000,"text":"Now you can also take the same approach"},{"time":1204000,"text":"to address problems in aging."},{"time":1207000,"text":"Where again the machinery is deteriorating now"},{"time":1209000,"text":"from competent machinery, it's going south."},{"time":1213000,"text":"Noise is increasing in the brain."},{"time":1215000,"text":"And learning modulation and control is deteriorating."},{"time":1218000,"text":"And you can actually look down on the brain of such an individual"},{"time":1220000,"text":"and witness a change in the time constants and space constants"},{"time":1223000,"text":"with which, for example, the brain is representing language again."},{"time":1226000,"text":"Just as the brain came out of chaos at the beginning,"},{"time":1229000,"text":"it's going back into chaos in the end."},{"time":1232000,"text":"This results in declines in memory"},{"time":1234000,"text":"in cognition, and in postural ability and agility."},{"time":1238000,"text":"It turns out you can train the brain of such an individual --"},{"time":1240000,"text":"this is a small population of such individuals --"},{"time":1243000,"text":"train equally intensively for about 30 hours."},{"time":1245000,"text":"These are 80- to 90-year-olds."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1248000,"text":"And what you see are substantial improvements of their immediate memory,"},{"time":1251000,"text":"of their ability to remember things after a delay,"},{"time":1253000,"text":"of their ability to control their attention,"},{"time":1255000,"text":"their language abilities and visual-spatial abilities."},{"time":1257000,"text":"The overall neuropsychological index"},{"time":1259000,"text":"of these trained individuals in this population"},{"time":1262000,"text":"is about two standard deviations."},{"time":1264000,"text":"That means that if you sit at the left side of the distribution,"},{"time":1266000,"text":"and I'm looking at your neuropyschological abilities,"},{"time":1269000,"text":"the average person has moved to the middle"},{"time":1271000,"text":"or the right side of the distribution."},{"time":1273000,"text":"It means that most people who are at risk for senility,"},{"time":1275000,"text":"more or less immediately,"},{"time":1277000,"text":"are now in a protected position."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1280000,"text":"My issues are to try to get to rescuing"},{"time":1283000,"text":"older citizens more completely and in larger numbers,"},{"time":1286000,"text":"because I think this can be done in this arena on a vast scale --"},{"time":1289000,"text":"and the same for kids."},{"time":1291000,"text":"My main interest is how to elaborate this science to address other maladies."},{"time":1294000,"text":"I'm specifically interested in things like autism,"},{"time":1296000,"text":"and cerebral palsy, these great childhood catastrophes."},{"time":1299000,"text":"And in older age conditions like Parkinsonism,"},{"time":1302000,"text":"and in other acquired impairments like schizophrenia."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1307000,"text":"Your issues as it relates to this science,"},{"time":1310000,"text":"is how to maintain your own high-functioning learning machine."},{"time":1313000,"text":"And of course, a well-ordered life"},{"time":1316000,"text":"in which learning is a continuous part of it, is key."},{"time":1318000,"text":"But also in your future is brain aerobics."},{"time":1321000,"text":"Get ready for it. It's going to be a part of every life"},{"time":1323000,"text":"not too far in the future,"},{"time":1325000,"text":"just like physical exercise"},{"time":1327000,"text":"is a part of every well organized life in the contemporary period."},{"time":1331000,"text":"The other way that we will ultimately come to consider this"},{"time":1335000,"text":"literature and the science that is important to you"},{"time":1338000,"text":"is in a consideration of how to nurture yourself."},{"time":1340000,"text":"Now that you know, now that science is telling us"},{"time":1343000,"text":"that you are in charge,"},{"time":1345000,"text":"that it's under your control,"},{"time":1347000,"text":"that your happiness, your well-being,"},{"time":1349000,"text":"your abilities, your capacities,"},{"time":1351000,"text":"are capable of continuous modification,"},{"time":1354000,"text":"continuous improvement,"},{"time":1356000,"text":"and you're the responsible agent and party."},{"time":1359000,"text":"Of course a lot of people will ignore this advice."},{"time":1361000,"text":"It will be a long time before they really understand it."},{"time":1363000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":1364000,"text":"Now that's another issue and not my fault."},{"time":1366000,"text":"Okay. Thank you."},{"time":1368000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}